  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large clay pot or Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and garlic and cook until the onion is translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the cumin, coriander, cinnamon, and cayenne pepper and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the fish fillet and cook for 2-3 minutes on each side, or until browned.",
    "Add the chicken broth and lemon juice, and bring to a simmer.",
